\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Did he ever take you out without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Well perhaps on an odd occasion but they were always together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 You don't ever remember any particular occasions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 If she was out at all would he stay in and look after you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 He would have done but she never went out anywhere and left us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Did you have any tasks that you had to carry out regularly at home to help your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 You didn't have any set jobs?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Did the older children help the younger ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 I suppose so, yes.
