\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Bacon and egg or something, yes, I don't know that I would take it because I was a very fickey person when I was a child.
