Yes, yes. Yes, we were all at home for midday meal and we would have the normal things, soup, meat, potatoes, pudding. And always had a pudding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Did your father come home for his lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Yes. Yes. He never took a breakfast but he always took the rest of his meals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 He didn't get his breakfast at his work did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 No. Uh huh, no he -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 You came home for your lunch from school, you'd go back to school, what would be your next meal then?
