\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Was it your father that tended the allotment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Yes. Yes. And my mother. And the family.
