\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Did you ever get any extra meat such as rabbits from poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 No. Definitely not, no. No.
