\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 What colour did he wear?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Black tailed coat. A black tailed coat, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 I thought they'd always wear a navy suit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 No. No, well you see he had black tails.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Who would attend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 And a tall hat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 The whole lot
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Who would attend the funeral, was it just the family or were there family and friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Family and friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Close friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Yes, I expect so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 When you were a child were you taken out visiting neighbours, friends or relati}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5788777\charrsid3623606 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 ns at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Who would take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 My mother. And my fathe
r if - on - on occasion. But mother was the one who was likely to take us out in the - in an afternoon to - you know, some of her friends for tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Did you visit your relations much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Not many of them, yes, but we visited my aunt - two aunts particularly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Were you taken out shopping?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Was that your mother again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Did you ever go out with just your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 I can't ever remember just going out with my father. I suppose he did take us out somewhere, but it - t
hey were always together, they were never separate.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Do you remember any other outings with your parents, such as a Bank Holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Oh yes, yes - at holidays we used to go away for picnics.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Where about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Well - down to Musselburgh or - ou
t to Colinton, and then we had a house in - in the country you see, mother had a - a cottage in Burntisland. And we used to go there every weekend, and then for summer holidays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Did you go by train?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 No, we went by boat mostly. We did go by train
 sometimes, but went across - on the Willie Muir from - Granton to Burntisland. And we did that practically every weekend during the summer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 How long would you stay when you were there on holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Two weeks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 That was during the summer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 As well as the weekends that you went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Which members of the family went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 All of us..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 All of the family went?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 What did you do when you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Well I don't know what - went for 
walks and - we had - played games and - just the usual things you would do at a very small country cottage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Would you play down on the sands?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 No. Well, we got - if we went to the sands that was a good bit away from the - the house. Be about a mi
le and a half or something. We used to go down periodically but - or down to the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5788777\charrsid3623606 pierots, you know, there was a p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 
ierot show on the - on the front. But - normally we would be up in the - the hills and - uh huh, a big hill then. We used to run up and down there and - you know, the usual things you would do, play football up - catch or runders or whatever it was.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Can you tell me how you spent Saturday in these days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 I should think I - perhaps be out playing in the morning and then in the afternoon usually went out with my father and mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Where about would you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 
Just round the shops. Either perhaps down Judson Street or - occasionally down the Kirkgate but I didn't like that place, there was always drunks there. Oh yes. On a Saturday afternoon, yes. I used to loathe it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Were there licensing hours at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 
Well - yes, there were licensing - licensing hours but I wouldn't know - what they were. But I never liked to be where there were drunks, and it was a pretty poor - quart - part of the - the town.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 How about a Sunday, what would you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Well, we didn't often go to church. I think we just more or less spent it at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Did you have different clothes to put on on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Yes, always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Did you play games on a Sunday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Never outside, no. Perhaps played about in the house but never out - we were never allowed out to play on Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Did your parents think it was wrong to play on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Yes, and it would have -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 What about working on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 
Mother didn't approve of that either. We weren't - if you had a hole in your stocking or anything, when I grew older you know, I used to have to go into the bedroom to - darn it, because mother didn't allow you to do these things
 on Sunday. The only time she gave way was during the war. The first world war, she knitted - a lot of socks and helmets and things and she did that sometimes on a Sunday, but it was because it was a war effort. Other times you wasn't allowed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 If you went to church was that with your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Did they both go or just your mother or just your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Both. Both, when they did go. Mother had been brought up very strictly when she was young she went an awful lot to church, she had to
 go five times on a Sunday to church and Sunday school and - Bible Class and all such thing, and she really said she got sickened of it so that she wasn't a very regular attender.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Which church was it you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Oh - Trinity college.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Did you go to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Yes, but I didn't go to that Sunday school because it was too far away. I did go for a while to a - a Sunday school in Lorne Street.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Were there any Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Yes. Yes. You went perhaps to Craigmore Castle. Or - just not very far away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Were there any other social activities organized by the church that you took part in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 No.
