Well it was very funny because we were invited to a party in - up in the house, and as he - my husband asked me to go out with him on the Tuesday, which I did, and then he asked me out on the Sunda
y. And from then on - from then on it was practically all the time.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Did you continue to go out with your other friends after you were courting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 No. No. Sort of dropped them, yes.
