ing by train to London, and - we thought we had a - a great secret, we'd run away from the - room, from the - the reception, and we were too early so we went to our new home, and sat there to wait 'til the time for the train. But when we got to the statio
n - a whole crowd of young ones were there and - in those days it was a case of - we booked a compartment, so they had it - gaily decorated out and ballo}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8081930\charrsid3623606 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 ns and - they gave us an awful time before we left, had confetti everywhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 You said you went to London, was that your destination or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 No, we were going to - France. We went to Paris. To - Lugano. To Florence and Venice. Menton. Back to - Paris.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 How long were you away for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10627508 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Three weeks. Nearly a month. Three weeks and a bit. And we came -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16398255 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4466894\charrsid3623606 Then back to Paris?
